    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle Street</name>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey<ptr target="uva.00482_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1885-11-25" rend="right">Nov: 25 '85<ptr target="uva.00482_n2"/></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>My dear W R T</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Thanks for the $5. "remembrance." Nothing very new with me. My sight is
                better&#8212;walking power slim, almost not at all&#8212;spirits buoyant. Glad to
                get your letters. As I write, we here are just through a dark November storm of
                three days, &#38; the sun is coming out. </p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
